    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Episodic Memory</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Specific past events with time/place context.</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2 space-y-1">
      <li>Representations: Experience logs; memory networks; embeddings</li>
      <li>Use cases: Dialogue continuity; personalization; robotics</li>
      <li>Traits: Dynamic, autobiographical, decays</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Procedural Memory</h2>
